description: Happy Belly Curbside Kitchen is a food truck that serves food so good it runs down your arm and puts a smile on your face. We proudly serve local, natural and organic products from our truck and our catering kitchen.We feature a 'Feel Good Food' menu that includes wholesome, all-natural, seasonal, organic foods. We have a Big Green Egg on our truck providing succulent meats and freshly grilled vegetables in addition to many other items, which are made to order on site. Like no other truck in Atlanta! with the most friendly people running it. :-)Everyone should have a Happy Belly!
name: Happy Belly Curbside Kitchen
